{"tid":319106,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"考慮讀中文/語文 Asso請入 HKCC>HKU SPACE>CCCU","createTime":"2017-07-12T14:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T11:53:28.000Z","uid":81572,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"907af37655fcbddc637cc9c06e0de8ff958d8583","tid":319106,"uid":81572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:19:44.000Z","msg":"以下是根據我多日資料蒐集得出結果<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHKCC&gt;&gt;&gt;HKU SPACE&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;CCCU<br />\n<br />\nHKCC 第一個sem科目比較多元，想高分要努力D，因為唔係所有人都係通才，It 丶批判思考、Communication可以死背對付，教授比分公平。poly會收大部份學生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHKU SPACE 好多人以為要好讀好多英文科，其實同另外兩間CC差唔多，不過佢文科唔係最出名，所以升大學比例相對於其他科來講比較低，所以我個人評價較低一點。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCCCU 每個學期都有一科通識科要讀，但唔係中文系自己開，好似係cccu開的，所以讀咩學系都要讀。<br />\n<br />\n排名最低原因係 賣盤同聽聞今年city冇續約所以學生連Locker有病睇醫生醫生福利都無得用。<br />\n上莊玩Ocamp的營長莊員容易上大學。詳情還在問師兄師姐。 <br />\n<br />\n利伸：我分數唔夠但有3322，見政府有錢資助，如果升唔到最後會入自資大學<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位同路人加油，祝大家前程錦繡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195e28f47190bc789cf370d9198be16cb20b4a5e","tid":319106,"uid":37600,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:36:32.000Z","msg":"無自資大學，得自資學位"},{"pid":"83859fd64336235c0c7d1a1461398fe2e5d60857","tid":319106,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:52:44.000Z","msg":"asso學生等於垃圾？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/293630/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/293630/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有堆asshole仔喺呢個po度比純正大學生圍剿緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作為asshole仔嘅你仲唔快啲過去增援?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30477166511aa5415e6ecfbe8a51f256049